{"tid":1619272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民信回教","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:09:59.000Z","uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33f44c6a6f65b4b31e5a5391605043ed62c75a02","tid":1619272,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"什葉派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0C7cOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0C7cOK.png&h=2e84262c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宗教可以帶面罩"},{"pid":"f0271845524c0ea9a83aafc59a63f18b3c5fb821","tid":1619272,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"奉至仁至慈的真主之名（بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ）<br />\n一切讚頌，全歸真主，全世界的主（الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ），<br />\n至仁至慈的主（الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ），<br />\n審判日的主（مَالِكِ يَوْمِ الدِّينِ）。<br />\n我們崇拜祢，只求祢佑助（إِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَإِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِينُ），<br />\n求祢引導我們上正路（اهْدِنَا الصِّرَاطَ الْمُسْتَقِيمَ），<br />\n祢所佑助者的路，不是受譴怒者的路，也不是迷誤者的路。（صِرَاطَ الَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا الضَّالِّينَ）。（一章：一至七節）"},{"pid":"044e45301f97de51254f2c11f946255c1b9ce776","tid":1619272,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">الله</span></span>"},{"pid":"b41d4be6aa53878fd8d19e739c0bfce4fd1efeb1","tid":1619272,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d877d23b89dbdb6ca5954f6ee9198962a04eb97e","tid":1619272,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"亞拉萬歲"},{"pid":"129eb71991b42351d0e757909e06fab02c0865ef","tid":1619272,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"係咪唔食得豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正有豬瘟"},{"pid":"5d7f12fe51937ab490d323ba2113f6f7e34b7ac8","tid":1619272,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"咁男人呢"},{"pid":"67c7bb063238987e5000b877c1c7f910e5084003","tid":1619272,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"129eb71991b42351d0e757909e06fab02c0865ef","tid":1619272,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"係咪唔食得豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正有豬瘟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"God knows"}]}